  ('IntexGlobal','BB5003','532ml Bell Bottle with Solid Handle','532ml-bell-bottle-with-solid-handle-bb5003','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','The 532ml Bell Bottle with Solid Handle combines modern design with practicality, making it the perfect companion for your daily hydration needs.',50,true,false,'["Available in 7 Colours: Choose from Black, Grey, White, Navy, Pink, Green, and Red, each with a solid powder-coated finish for a sleek, modern look.", "532ml Vacuum Bottle: Double-walled insulation keeps your beverages cold for longer, ensuring a refreshing drink whenever you need it.", "Solid Handle Lid: The bottle features a sturdy, ergonomic handle for easy portability, making it ideal for on-the-go hydration.", "Premium 304 Stainless Steel: Made with durable stainless steel inner and outer layers, and a copper-plated lining for enhanced insulation and durability.", "100% Leakproof & Puncture/Rust Resistant: Built to withstand everyday use, ensuring your drink stays secure and your bottle remains in excellent condition.", "Customizable: Perfect for laser engraving or printing, ideal for personalized gifts, branding, or promotional products.", "Dishwasher Safe: Easy to clean (exclusive of decoration).", "Not Suitable for Hot or Carbonated Beverages or Food: Best for cold drinks.", "Eco-Friendly Packaging: Each bottle is individually packed in an eco-friendly BELL branded carton."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "25.8 x 7.5 x 7.5 cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/bb5003/bb5003-black.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/bb5003/bb5003-green.webp"}, {"name": "Grey", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/bb5003/bb5003-grey.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbe