  ('IntexGlobal','BB5004','532ml Bell Bottle with Sipper Handle','532ml-bell-bottle-with-sipper-handle-bb5004','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','Introducing the 532ml Bell Bottle with Sipper Handle, designed for ease of use and durability, this vacuum-insulated bottle keeps your drinks cold for longer while offering a practical sipper handle for convenient sipping on the go.',50,true,false,'["Available in 7 Colours: Choose from Black, Grey, White, Navy, Pink, Green, and Red, each with a solid powder-coated finish for a sleek and modern appearance.", "532ml Vacuum Bottle: Double-walled insulation ensures your drinks stay cold for extended periods.", "Sipper Handle Lid: Features a practical sipper handle for easy drinking, making it ideal for active lifestyles.", "Premium 304 Stainless Steel: Made from durable stainless steel inner and outer layers, with a copper-plated lining for superior insulation and durability.", "100% Leakproof & Puncture/Rust Resistant: Designed for long-lasting use with a leakproof construction and rust-resistant finish.", "Customizable: Perfect for laser engraving or printing, making it ideal for personalized gifts, promotions, or corporate branding.", "Dishwasher Safe: Easy to clean (exclusive of decoration).", "Not Suitable for Hot or Carbonated Beverages or Food: Best used for cold drinks.", "Eco-Friendly Packaging: Each bottle is individually packed in an eco-friendly BELL branded carton."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "25.8 x 7.5 x 7.5 cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/bb5004/bb5004-black.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/bb5004/bb5004-green.webp"}, {"name": "Grey", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/bb5004/bb5004-grey.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "