  ('IntexGlobal','BB5005','Bell 3-In-1 Copper Vacuum Bottle Kit 950ml','bell-3-in-1-copper-vacuum-bottle-kit-950ml-bb5005','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','The Bell 3-In-1 Copper Vacuum Bottle Kit is your ultimate hydration companion, engineered for versatility, durability, and eco-conscious living. Crafted from recycled stainless steel and designed with a triple-lid system, this 950ml insulated bottle adapts effortlessly to every drinking style while delivering long-lasting temperature control.',25,true,false,'["Triple screw-on lid system includes straw lid for easy sipping, chug lid for fast hydration, and flip-top lid for controlled pouring or secure storage.", "Generous 950ml (1L) capacity for all-day hydration.", "Made from recycled stainless steel, supporting sustainability without compromising strength or performance.", "Double-wall stainless steel construction with copper vacuum insulation keeps drinks cold for up to 48 hours and hot for up to 12 hours.", "Sleek powder-coated finish adds modern style while enhancing durability and grip.", "Condensation-free exterior prevents moisture buildup for comfortable handling.", "Built for active lifestyles, travel, work, and outdoor adventures."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "9cm(w) x 25.4cm(h) x 10.6cm(d)"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Wh", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/bb5005/bb5005-wh.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/1l-stainless-steel-double-wall-bottle-with-3-lids/');
