  ('IntexGlobal','DUFB34','Clear PVC Drawstring Bag','clear-pvc-drawstring-bag-dufb34','Bags','Drawstring Bags','The Clear PVC Drawstring Bag is a sleek and functional promotional item, perfect for events, stadiums, concerts, and security-compliant venues. Its transparent design ensures quick visibility of contents, while the colored accents add a stylish touch.',250,true,false,'["Transparent PVC Material: Allows for easy visibility and meets security requirements for events and venues.", "Drawstring Closure: Securely keeps items in place while allowing quick access.", "Coloured Accents: Stylish trim on the top and bottom for added appeal and branding opportunities.", "Spacious Interior: Ideal for carrying essentials like water bottles, snacks, or personal items.", "Durable & Easy to Clean: Water-resistant and wipeable for effortless maintenance.", "Large Branding Area: Perfect for screen printing logos, event names, or promotional messages.", "Versatile Use: Great for concerts, sporting events, stadiums, trade shows, and corporate giveaways."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "39 (w) x 49 (h) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/dufb34/dufb34-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/dufb34/dufb34-green.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/dufb34/dufb34-red.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,1.2,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/clear-pvc-drawstring-bag/');
