  ('IntexGlobal','JUTB03','Large Jute Tote Bag With Gusset','large-jute-tote-bag-with-gusset-jutb03','Bags','Jute Bags','The Large Jute Tote Bag with Gusset is a durable and reusable promotional tote, perfect for retail stores, corporate gifting, and eco-conscious branding. Made from natural hessian jute, it features a contrast-colored gusset and matching cotton handles, adding a stylish touch to its functionality.',250,true,false,'["Premium Natural Hessian Jute: Strong, biodegradable, and environmentally friendly.", "Contrast-Coloured Gusset: Adds a stylish accent while increasing storage space.", "Matching Cotton Handles: Soft and reinforced for comfortable carrying.", "Spacious Design: Ideal for shopping, events, or daily essentials.", "Durable & Reusable: Built to withstand frequent use, promoting sustainability."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "36(w) x 41(h) x 12(g)cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/jutb03/jutb03-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,3.83,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/large-jute-tote-bag-with-gusset/');
