  ('IntexGlobal','JUTB11','Jute Boutique Bag With Gusset','jute-boutique-bag-with-gusset-jutb11','Bags','Jute Bags','The Jute Boutique Bag with Gusset is a stylish and sustainable promotional tote, made from natural hessian jute. This bag is designed for durability and everyday use, with a gusset for extra storage capacity and wider natural cotton handles for enhanced comfort.',250,true,false,'["Premium Natural Hessian Jute: Strong, biodegradable, and environmentally friendly.", "Gusseted Design: Provides extra space, making it ideal for carrying larger or bulkier items.", "Wider Natural Cotton Handles: Soft and reinforced for comfortable carrying.", "Durable & Reusable: Built to withstand frequent use while promoting sustainability.", "Large Branding Area: Perfect for printing  of logos, slogans, or promotional messages."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "40(w) x 32(h) x 12(g)cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/jutb11/jutb11-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,2.94,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/jute-boutique-bag-with-gusset/');
