  ('IntexGlobal','LIFE110','Chill Wine Bag With Gel Wine Carrier','chill-wine-bag-with-gel-wine-carrier-life110','Bags','Wine Carriers','The Chill Wine Bag with Gel is a sleek and functional solution for keeping wine chilled on the go. Designed with a built-in gel freezing layer, this bag ensures your wine stays at the perfect temperature, making it ideal for picnics, outdoor events, and corporate gifting.',250,true,false,'["Built-in Gel Freezing Technology: Keeps wine bottles cool for extended periods.", "Stylish & Durable Design: Perfect for gifting, retail, or event giveaways.", "Fits One Standard Wine Bottle: Designed to accommodate most wine bottles securely.", "Easy to Use: Simply freeze the bag before use for optimal chilling performance.", "Portable & Reusable: A practical and eco-conscious alternative to single-use wine coolers."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "25 (w) x 9 (h) x 9 (d) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/life110/life110-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,2.39,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/chill-wine-bag-with-gel/');
