  ('IntexGlobal','NEOP52','15" Premium Sublimated Neoprene Laptop Sleeve With Zipper Tech Accessory','15-premium-sublimated-neoprene-laptop-sleeve-with-zipper-tech-accessory-neop52','Tech','Tech Accessories','Introducing the 15" Premium Sublimated Neoprene Laptop Sleeve With Zipper, designed for superior protection and style. Made from high-quality neoprene, this sleeve offers a soft, durable, and lightweight solution to keep your laptop safe from scratches, dust, and minor impacts. The smooth zipper closure ensures a secure fit, making it perfect for work, travel, or daily use.',1,true,false,'["Premium Neoprene Material – Soft, flexible, and protective", "Smooth Zipper Closure – Secure and easy access to your laptop", "Scratch & Dust Resistant – Shields your laptop from everyday wear", "Slim & Lightweight – Easy to carry or slide into a bag", "Perfect Fit for 15\" Laptops – Snug and secure fit"]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "37 (w) x 27 (h)cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Custom", "hex": "", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,null,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/16-premium-neoprene-laptop-sleeve-with-zipper/');
