  ('IntexGlobal','OC2016B','500ml Japanese Style Vacuum Bottle','500ml-japanese-style-vacuum-bottle-oc2016b','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','The 500ml Japanese Style Vacuum Bottle combines sleek aesthetics with superior insulation, offering a modern and functional hydration solution. Designed with minimalist Japanese-inspired styling, this bottle ensures optimal heat retention, making it ideal for hot and cold beverages throughout the day.',250,true,false,'["500ml Capacity: Perfect for daily hydration.", "Double-Walled Vacuum Insulation: Keeps drinks hot or cold for extended periods.", "Premium Stainless Steel Construction: Durable, lightweight, and resistant to wear.", "Minimalist Japanese-Inspired Design: Sleek and stylish for a sophisticated look.", "Leak-Proof Lid: Prevents spills and ensures secure transportation.", "Compact & Portable: Ideal for work, travel, and outdoor activities."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "6.8(W) x 21(L)cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc2016b/oc2016b-black.webp"}, {"name": "Cream", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc2016b/oc2016b-cream.webp"}, {"name": "Olive", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc2016b/oc2016b-olive.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc2016b/oc2016b-red.webp"}, {"name": "Teal", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc2016b/oc2016b-teal.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,5.43,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/500ml-japanese-style-vacuum-bottle/');
