  ('IntexGlobal','OC2402','Genesis Glass Bottle','genesis-glass-bottle-oc2402','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','The Genesis Glass Bottle combines premium craftsmanship with a sleek, modern design, making it the ideal sustainable alternative for those who value both style and environmental responsibility. Crafted from high-quality glass, this bottle offers a refined and reusable solution for everyday hydration.',250,true,false,'["Premium Glass Construction: Ensures durability and a sophisticated, high-end look.", "Sleek & Modern Design: Perfect for professionals, fitness enthusiasts, and eco-conscious consumers.", "Reusable & Sustainable: A stylish alternative to single-use plastic bottles.", "Leak-Proof Lid: Secures beverages for on-the-go convenience.", "Easy to Clean: Designed for effortless maintenance and long-term use.", "Custom Branding Available: Can be personalized with logos or designs for promotional use."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "7.4 x 17.3 cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc2402/oc2402-black.webp"}, {"name": "Grey", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc2402/oc2402-grey.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc2402/oc2402-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Pink", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc2402/oc2402-pink.webp"}, {"name": "Teal", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc2402/oc2402-teal.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc2402/oc2402-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,5.44,28,'indent_sea','Intex',