  ('IntexGlobal','OC31X293','Terry Wrist Sweatband Sport Product','terry-wrist-sweatband-sport-product-oc31x293','Outdoor & Lifestyle','Sports Products','The Terry Wrist Sweatband is a comfortable and functional accessory designed for sports, workouts, and outdoor activities. Made from lightweight terry elastic (18g), it is breathable, stretchable, and highly absorbent, making it ideal for keeping sweat off hands and wrists during intense physical activities.',1,true,false,'["Lightweight Terry Elastic Material (18g): Soft, breathable, and designed for all-day comfort.", "Sweat Absorbent: Helps keep hands dry for better grip during workouts or sports.", "Stretchable & Snug Fit: Provides a secure, non-slip feel for any wrist size.", "Durable & Long-Lasting: Designed for repeated use without losing elasticity.", "Ideal for Sports & Fitness: Perfect for running, gym sessions, yoga, tennis, and other athletic activities.", "Custom Branding Available: Can be printed or embroidered with logos for promotional use."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "7.5 x 7.5 cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc31x293/oc31x293-black.webp"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc31x293/oc31x293-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc31x293/oc31x293-green.webp"}, {"name": "Grey", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc31x293/oc31x293-grey.webp"}, {"name": "Light Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc31x293/oc31x293-light-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Light Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2