  ('IntexGlobal','OC5601','Swimming Caps - Silicone Sport Product','swimming-caps-silicone-sport-product-oc5601','Outdoor & Lifestyle','Sports Products','The Silicone Swimming Caps provide a sleek and secure fit, designed to protect hair from chlorine and reduce drag in the water. Made from high-quality silicone, these caps offer durability, flexibility, and optimal hydrodynamics, making them perfect for competitive and recreational swimmers alike.',250,true,false,'["Premium Silicone Material: Stretchable, long-lasting, and resistant to tearing.", "Snug & Secure Fit: Reduces water resistance and enhances swimming performance.", "Protects Hair from Chlorine & Chemicals: Keeps hair dry and shielded during swimming.", "Smooth & Hydrodynamic Design: Improves glide and speed in the water.", "Comfortable & Easy to Wear: Soft, flexible fit without pulling on hair.", "Custom Branding Available: Can be printed with logos or designs for promotional use."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "19 x 22cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc5601/oc5601-black.webp"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc5601/oc5601-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc5601/oc5601-green.webp"}, {"name": "Grey", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc5601/oc5601-grey.webp"}, {"name": "Hot Pink", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc5601/oc5601-hot-pink.webp"}, {"name": "Light Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc5601/oc5601-light-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Navy