  ('IntexGlobal','OC721908','Sigma RPET Sunglasses','sigma-rpet-sunglasses-oc721908','Outdoor & Lifestyle','Sunglasses','Look good while doing good with Sigma RPET Sunglasses — a perfect fusion of modern style and eco-conscious design. Crafted from recycled polyethylene terephthalate (RPET), these sunglasses reduce environmental impact without compromising on quality or fashion. Whether you''re at a beach event, festival, or outdoor promo campaign, they’re the ideal statement piece for environmentally aware brands an',250,true,false,'["Made from recycled RPET for reduced environmental impact.", "Sleek, modern frame design for a fashionable look.", "Lightweight and comfortable for all-day wear.", "UV400 lenses for essential sun protection.", "Ideal for eco-conscious events, promotions, and giveaways."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "14.5 x 4.5 x 3.2 cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Custom", "hex": "", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,3.35,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/sigma-rpet-sunglasses/');
