  ('IntexGlobal','OCA100','Oc Chef / Waiters Apron Home Decor','oc-chef-waiters-apron-home-decor-oca100','Home & Living','Home Decor','The OC Chef/Waiter’s Apron is a classic choice for professionals in the culinary and hospitality industry. Combining durability, comfort, and functionality, this full-length bib-style apron is a dependable work essential.',25,true,false,'["Professional Design: Classic black and white apron with a clean and polished look, ideal for chefs, waitstaff, and kitchen staff.", "Durable Material: Made from a premium blend of 65% polyester and 35% cotton in 280gsm twill fabric, ensuring strength and longevity.", "Functional Front Pocket: Convenient single front pocket for easy access to essential tools and accessories.", "Adjustable Neck Strap: Provides a customizable fit for maximum comfort during long hours.", "Full-Length Coverage: Protects clothing from spills and stains, making it perfect for busy kitchens or dining areas."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "83cm x 71cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oca100/oca100-black.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oca100/oca100-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/oc-chef-waiters-apron/');
