  ('IntexGlobal','OCAEM101','Expandable Boot Organizer Car Accessory','expandable-boot-organizer-car-accessory-ocaem101','Tools & Auto','Car Accessories','The Expandable Boot Organizer is a versatile and practical car accessory, designed to keep vehicle trunks neat and organized. Made from 80gsm non-woven polypropylene material, this organizer features three large compartments, an outside mesh pocket, and sturdy plastic handles, making it ideal for storing groceries, tools, sports gear, and travel essentials.',250,true,false,'["Durable 80gsm Non-Woven Polypropylene Material: Lightweight yet strong for long-lasting use.", "Three Large Compartments: Provides ample space for organizing various items.", "Outside Mesh Pocket: Offers easy access to small essentials.", "Plastic Handles: Ensures a comfortable and secure grip for carrying.", "Expandable & Collapsible Design: Expands for maximum storage and folds flat for easy storage when not in use.", "Ideal for Vehicle Organization: Great for keeping trunks tidy and preventing items from shifting during travel.", "Custom Branding Available: Can be printed with logos or designs for promotional use."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "33 (w) x 33(h) 56 (D) (open)"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocaem101/ocaem101-black.webp"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocaem101/ocaem101-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocaem101/ocaem101-green.webp"}, {"name": "Maroon", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocaem101/ocaem101-maroon.webp"}, {"name": "Pink", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/pr