  ('IntexGlobal','OCBAB104','Non-Woven Essential Briefcase Tote With Zipper Closure Tote Bag','non-woven-essential-briefcase-tote-with-zipper-closure-tote-bag-ocbab104','Bags','Tote Bags','The Non-Woven Essential Briefcase Tote is a spacious and durable promotional bag designed for business, events, and everyday use. Its zippered closure and large size make it perfect for carrying documents, conference materials, or personal essentials while showcasing your brand.',250,true,false,'["Durable 80gsm Non-Woven Material: Lightweight yet sturdy for reliable use.", "Oversized Design: Measures 51cm x 31cm with a 16cm gusset, providing ample storage space.", "Zipper Closure: Securely keeps contents protected, making it ideal for work or travel.", "Comfortable Shoulder Straps: Designed for easy carrying throughout the day.", "Available in Multiple Colors: Choose from a variety of shades to match your branding needs.", "Eco-Friendly & Reusable: A sustainable alternative to plastic bags, promoting green initiatives.", "Large Branding Area: Perfect for screen printing logos, business names, or promotional messages."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "5 1 (w) x 41 (h) with 16 cm gussets"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbab104/ocbab104-black.webp"}, {"name": "Mainjpg", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbab104/ocbab104-mainjpg.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbab104/ocbab104-red.webp"}, {"name": "Royal Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbab104/ocbab104-royal-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Royal", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400