  ('IntexGlobal','OCBAB105','Non-Woven Laundry Duffel Bag With Over The Shoulder Strap','non-woven-laundry-duffel-bag-with-over-the-shoulder-strap-ocbab105','Bags','Tote Bags','The Non-Woven Laundry Duffel Bag is a practical and eco-friendly promotional item, ideal for dorms, gyms, hotels, or travel. Its durable design and over-the-shoulder strap make carrying laundry effortless while providing excellent branding opportunities.',250,true,false,'["Durable 80gsm Non-Woven Material: Lightweight yet strong for carrying laundry or bulky items.", "Spacious Design: Measures 25cm x 81cm, offering ample storage capacity.", "Drawstring Closure: Securely keeps contents in place while making it easy to open and close.", "Over-the-Shoulder Strap: Ensures comfortable carrying and hands-free convenience.", "Eco-Friendly & Reusable: A sustainable alternative to plastic bags, promoting green living.", "Large Branding Area: Perfect for screen printing logos, slogans, or promotional messages."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "50 (w) x 81 (h) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbab105/ocbab105-black.webp"}, {"name": "Mainjpg", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbab105/ocbab105-mainjpg.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbab105/ocbab105-red.webp"}, {"name": "Royaljpg", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbab105/ocbab105-royaljpg.webp"}, {"name": "Royal", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbab105/ocbab105-royal.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,1.98,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/non-woven-laundry-d