  ('IntexGlobal','OCBAB109','Full Colour Print Landscape Bag','full-colour-print-landscape-bag-ocbab109','Bags','Paper Bags','The Full Colour Print Landscape Bag is a premium promotional tote, designed for maximum brand visibility and functionality. With a full-colour laminated finish, this bag provides vibrant, high-quality printing, making it perfect for corporate events, trade shows, retail packaging, and luxury branding.',1,true,false,'["High-Quality Full-Colour Printing: Ensures vibrant, edge-to-edge customization for striking brand visibility.", "Durable Laminated Material: Designed for longevity, providing a sleek and professional finish.", "Landscape Orientation: Ideal for carrying brochures, promotional materials, and retail products.", "Strong Handles: Reinforced for durability and comfortable carrying.", "Spacious & Functional: Perfect for trade shows, corporate gifting, and premium retail packaging.", "Large Branding Area: Ideal for digital print, or custom artwork, ensuring a standout promotional presence."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "33 (w) x 25 (h) with 13 cm gussets"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbab109/ocbab109-black.webp"}, {"name": "Grey", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbab109/ocbab109-grey.webp"}, {"name": "Hunter Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbab109/ocbab109-hunter-green.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbab109/ocbab109-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbab109/ocbab109-red.webp"}, {"name": "Royal", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c