  ('IntexGlobal','OCBBC108','Cotton Wine Bottle Gift Tote Wine Carrier','cotton-wine-bottle-gift-tote-wine-carrier-ocbbc108','Bags','Wine Carriers','The Cotton Wine Bottle Gift Tote is a durable and eco-friendly solution for wine gifting, retail, and promotional events. Made from 180gsm cotton fabric, this reusable tote offers a natural, stylish, and sustainable alternative to traditional wine packaging.',250,true,false,'["Premium 180gsm Cotton Fabric: Strong, reusable, and environmentally friendly.", "Fits One Standard Wine Bottle: Perfect for gifting, retail packaging, and special events.", "Durable Cotton Handles: Comfortable and reinforced for secure carrying.", "Natural & Elegant Design: Complements any occasion with a clean and sophisticated look."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "8(w) x 27(h) x 8(d) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbbc108/ocbbc108-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,1.68,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/cotton-wine-bottle-gift-tote/');
