  ('IntexGlobal','OCBBP1011','Calico Pocket Jute Tote Bag','calico-pocket-jute-tote-bag-ocbbp1011','Bags','Jute Bags','The Calico Pocket Jute Tote Bag is a premium eco-friendly promotional tote, combining the durability of natural hessian jute with a cotton front pocket for custom branding. Designed for retail, corporate gifting, and sustainable promotions, this bag offers a natural look with functional elegance.',250,true,false,'["Cotton Front Pocket: Provides a smooth surface for high-quality screen printing or embroidery of logos and designs.", "Reinforced Jute Handles: Sturdy and comfortable for everyday carrying.", "Spacious & Durable: Ideal for shopping, trade shows, corporate events, or daily use.", "Stylish Boutique Design: The contrast between jute and cotton creates a sophisticated and natural aesthetic."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "45cm (w) x 33cm (h) x 6cm (G)"}, {"name": "Natural Hessian Jute Material", "value": "Strong, biodegradable, and eco-conscious."}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbbp1011/ocbbp1011-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,4.1,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/calico-pocket-jute-tote-bag/');
