  ('IntexGlobal','OCBMS118','Single Bottle Wine Bag Wine Carrier','single-bottle-wine-bag-wine-carrier-ocbms118','Bags','Wine Carriers','The Single Bottle Wine Bag is an elegant and eye-catching promotional item, perfect for wineries, corporate gifts, and retail packaging. Made from 80gsm non-woven material with full-colour lamination, this bag enhances branding while providing a stylish and reusable solution for gifting wine bottles.',1,true,false,'["Durable 80gsm Non-Woven Material: Strong, lightweight, and built for repeated use.", "Full-Colour Laminated Print: High-impact branding with vibrant, edge-to-edge customization.", "Perfect Fit for One Bottle: Designed to securely hold and present a single wine bottle.", "Reinforced Handles: Ensures a comfortable and secure grip for carrying.", "Large Branding Area: Ideal for showcasing logos, winery names, event details, or promotional artwork."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "13 (w) x 30 (h) x 10 (d) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Custom", "hex": "", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,null,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/single-bottle-wine-bag/');
