  ('IntexGlobal','OCBMS121','Full Colour Printed Tote Bag','full-colour-printed-tote-bag-ocbms121','Bags','Tote Bags','The Full Colour Printed Tote Bag is a high-impact, laminated non-woven promotional bag, perfect for trade shows, retail, and corporate giveaways. With its wider gusset and full-colour customization, this bag offers both functionality and maximum brand visibility.',1,true,false,'["Durable 80gsm Non-Woven Material: Lightweight yet strong for everyday use.", "Full-Colour Laminated Print: High-quality, edge-to-edge printing for vibrant branding.", "Spacious Design: 31cm (W) x 33cm (H) x 20cm (Gusset) for carrying larger items.", "Wider Gusset: Provides extra storage capacity, making it perfect for shopping or event materials.", "Reinforced Handles: Ensures comfortable carrying and long-lasting durability.", "Large Branding Area: Ideal for printing logos, marketing messages, or custom artwork in stunning full colour."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "31(w) x 33(h) x 20(g) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbms121/ocbms121-black.webp"}, {"name": "Bottle Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbms121/ocbms121-bottle-green.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbms121/ocbms121-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbms121/ocbms121-red.webp"}, {"name": "Royal", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbms121/ocbms121-royal.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbms121/ocbms121-white.we