  ('IntexGlobal','OCBMS130','Shopping Bag Extra Large Non Woven','shopping-bag-extra-large-non-woven-ocbms130','Bags','Tote Bags','The Extra Large Non-Woven Shopping Bag is a practical and eco-friendly promotional item, perfect for retail, grocery shopping, trade shows, and everyday use. Its sturdy design and generous size make it ideal for carrying bulkier items while promoting your brand.',250,true,false,'["Durable 80gsm Non-Woven Material: Strong and reusable, providing a sustainable alternative to plastic bags.", "Spacious Design: Measures 33cm x 38cm with a 25cm gusset and base, offering ample storage capacity.", "Reinforced Longer Straps: Designed for extra strength and comfortable carrying of heavier loads.", "Eco-Friendly & Reusable: Helps reduce plastic waste, making it a great choice for green initiatives.", "Large Branding Area: Ideal for printing logos, slogans, or promotional messages for maximum visibility."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "33(w) x 38(h) x 25(d) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Burgundy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbms130/ocbms130-burgundy.webp"}, {"name": "Charcoal", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbms130/ocbms130-charcoal.webp"}, {"name": "Chocolate", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbms130/ocbms130-chocolate.webp"}, {"name": "Dark Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbms130/ocbms130-dark-green.webp"}, {"name": "Khaki", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbms130/ocbms130-khaki.webp"}, {"name": "Lime Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbms13