  ('IntexGlobal','OCC0014','Plain Ceramic Mug 300ml','plain-ceramic-mug-300ml-occ0014','Drinkware','Mugs','The 300ml Plain Ceramic Mug is a classic and functional drinkware option, perfect for home, office, cafés, and promotional branding. With its clean white finish, this mug is an excellent choice for hot and cold beverages, making it ideal for daily use and corporate promotions.',250,true,false,'["300ml Capacity: Perfect for coffee, tea, and other hot or cold drinks.", "Classic White Finish: A clean and simple design suitable for all settings.", "Comfortable Handle: Ensures a secure and easy grip.", "Versatile for Any Occasion: Ideal for office desks, cafés, and home use."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "9.7cm H  x 8.8cm Dia"}, {"name": "Durable Ceramic Construction", "value": "Designed for long-lasting use."}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/occ0014/occ0014-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,2.73,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/plain-ceramic-mug-300ml/');
