  ('IntexGlobal','OCC018','Recycled Cotton Tote Bag','recycled-cotton-tote-bag-occ018','Bags','Cotton Tote Bags','The Recycled Cotton Tote Bag is an eco-conscious and stylish choice for businesses looking to promote sustainability. Made from 65% recycled cotton, this bag reduces waste while offering a practical and reusable solution for everyday use.',250,true,false,'["Eco-Friendly 140gsm Material: Made from 65% recycled cotton and 35% regular cotton, reducing environmental impact.", "Durable & Reusable: Sturdy construction ensures long-term use, making it a great alternative to plastic bags.", "Long Handles: Designed for comfortable carrying over the shoulder, perfect for daily errands.", "Spacious & Versatile: Ideal for grocery shopping, trade fairs, events, or everyday use.", "Customizable Branding Area: Large surface for screen printing logos or promotional messages."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "38 x 42cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/occ018/occ018-navy.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,1.35,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/recycled-cotton-tote-bag/');
