  ('IntexGlobal','OCHCD01','Nixson Two Tone Canvas Duffle Bag','nixson-two-tone-canvas-duffle-bag-ochcd01','Bags','Tote Bags','Perfect for weekend getaways or daily adventures, the Nixson Two-Tone Canvas Duffle Bag combines durability and practicality with timeless design.',50,true,false,'["Durable Material: Made from 100% cotton 430gsm canvas, ensuring long-lasting reliability and sturdiness.", "Spacious Capacity: Offers a generous 50-liter capacity to fit all your essentials for any trip.", "Detachable Shoulder Strap: Adjustable and detachable for comfortable carrying options.", "Stylish Two-Tone Design: Available in Navy/White, Red/White, and Black/White for a classic look.", "Convenient Storage: Features inner and outer pockets for easy organization of your belongings.", "Customizable Print Area: 15cm x 13cm print size, ideal for adding personalized designs or branding."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "25.8 x 47 cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ochcd01/ochcd01-black.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ochcd01/ochcd01-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ochcd01/ochcd01-red.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/nixson-two-tone-canvas-duffle-bag/');
