  ('IntexGlobal','OCNRPC01','Recycled Paper Playing Cards Game & Puzzle','recycled-paper-playing-cards-game-puzzle-ocnrpc01','Toys & Games','Games & Puzzles','The Recycled Paper Playing Cards set is a sustainable and entertaining promotional item, perfect for eco-conscious branding, corporate giveaways, and event promotions. Made from recycled paper, this standard 52-card deck comes in a kraft paper box, providing an environmentally friendly alternative to traditional playing cards.',250,true,false,'["Made from Recycled Paper: A sustainable choice that reduces environmental impact.", "Standard 52-Card Deck: Includes all four suits plus jokers for a complete playing experience.", "Durable Kraft Paper Box: Protects the deck while maintaining an eco-friendly look.", "Compact & Portable: Ideal for travel, game nights, and social gatherings.", "Great for All Ages & Occasions: Perfect for casual play, tournaments, or promotional giveaways.", "Custom Branding Available: Can be printed with logos or designs on the box for promotional use."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "6.5cm W x 9cm H"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocnrpc01/ocnrpc01-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,0.72,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/recycled-paper-playing-cards/');
