  ('IntexGlobal','OCP721707','Classic Mug','classic-mug-ocp721707','Drinkware','Mugs','The Classic Mug is a sleek and stylish 420ml ceramic mug featuring a natural cork base for a modern touch. Designed for both functionality and aesthetics, this mug is perfect for home, office, cafés, and promotional branding.',250,true,false,'["420ml Capacity: Ideal for coffee, tea, and other hot beverages.", "Durable Ceramic Construction: Ensures long-lasting use with a smooth finish.", "Natural Cork Base: Adds a stylish look while protecting surfaces from heat and scratches.", "Comfortable Handle: Designed for an easy and secure grip.", "Modern & Elegant Design: A perfect mix of classic and contemporary style.", "Handwash Recommended: Helps maintain the quality and longevity of the mug."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "9cm (D) x 11cm (H)"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocp721707/ocp721707-black.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocp721707/ocp721707-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,2.52,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/classic-mug/');
