  ('IntexGlobal','OCP781796','Bondi Cocktail Shaker Bar Accessory','bondi-cocktail-shaker-bar-accessory-ocp781796','Barware','Bar Accessories','The Bondi Cocktail Shaker is a premium stainless steel shaker, designed for home mixologists, bartenders, and cocktail enthusiasts. With a 550ml capacity, this stylish and functional shaker is perfect for crafting cocktails at home, bars, restaurants, or events. It comes elegantly packaged in a gift box, making it an excellent corporate gift or promotional giveaway.',250,true,false,'["High-Quality Stainless Steel: Durable, rust-resistant, and built for long-lasting use.", "550ml Capacity: Ideal for mixing a variety of cocktails.", "Classic & Stylish Design: A sleek and professional look for any bar setup.", "Secure & Leak-Proof Lid: Ensures smooth and mess-free cocktail shaking.", "Gift Box Packaging: Perfect for corporate gifts, promotions, or special occasions.", "Custom Branding Available: Can be personalized with logos or designs for promotional use."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "8.7cm x 21.5 cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Silver", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocp781796/ocp781796-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,6.51,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/bondi-cocktail-shaker/');
