  ('IntexGlobal','PAT08','Velvet Pouch For Usb Drive','velvet-pouch-for-usb-drive-pat08','Tech','USB Flash Drives','The Velvet Pouch is a stylish and practical accessory, perfect for enhancing the presentation and protection of your USB drives. Note : USB prices change frequently. Please contact our sales team for the latest price quote.',1,true,false,'["Soft Velvet Material: Provides a luxurious feel while protecting USB drives from scratches and dust.", "Drawstring Closure: Ensures secure storage and easy access to your USB drive.", "Compact Design: Lightweight and portable, making it perfect for gifting or promotional use.", "Versatile Use: Ideal for USB drives, small accessories, or as part of a branded gift set.", "Customizable Option: Available in various colors or with branding upon request for a personalized touch."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "(Small) 7.01 x 11 cm, (Large) 8.99 x 13 cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/pat08/pat08-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,null,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/velvet-pouch-for-usb-drive/');
