  ('IntexGlobal','PAT200','Wooden Swivel Drive','wooden-swivel-drive-pat200','Tech','USB Flash Drives','The Wooden Swivel USB Flash Drive is a sustainable and functional storage solution, perfect for environmentally conscious businesses and individuals. Note : USB prices change frequently. Please contact our sales team for the latest price quote.',1,true,false,'["Eco-Friendly Wooden Body: Made from natural wood, offering a stylish and sustainable alternative to traditional USB drives.", "Durable Metal Swivel Band: Protects the USB connector when not in use, adding durability and a sleek touch.", "Compact and Portable: Lightweight design makes it easy to carry, perfect for everyday use or promotional events.", "Customizable Surface: Ideal for engraving or printing logos, making it a standout promotional item or personalized gift."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "5.6cm W x 1.9cm H x 1cm L"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/pat200/pat200-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,null,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/wooden-swivel-drive/');
