  ('IntexGlobal','PAT201','Classic Swivel Drive 3.0','classic-swivel-drive-3-0-pat201','Tech','USB Flash Drives','The Classic Swivel Drive 3.0 is the ultimate USB flash drive, combining practicality, style, and affordability. Its timeless design makes it a favorite for both personal and promotional use. Note : USB prices change frequently. Please contact our sales team for the latest price quote.',1,true,false,'["Swivel Design: The rotating aluminum band protects the USB connector when not in use, eliminating the need for a cap.", "USB 3.0 Technology: Ensures faster data transfer speeds, perfect for storing and accessing files efficiently.", "Durable Construction: Features a sturdy aluminum swivel band, with an option to upgrade to a steel band for enhanced durability and style.", "Compact and Portable: Lightweight and easy to carry, ideal for work, school, or travel.", "Customizable Surface: Perfect for branding with logos or designs, making it an excellent promotional item."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "5.6cm W x 1.9cm H x 1cm L"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/pat201/pat201-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,null,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/classic-swivel-drive-3-0/');
