  ('IntexGlobal','PAT222','Silver Metal Swivel Drive','silver-metal-swivel-drive-pat222','Tech','USB Flash Drives','The Silver Metal Swivel USB Flash Drive combines elegance and practicality, making it a premium choice for personal use or corporate gifting. Note : USB prices change frequently. Please contact our sales team for the latest price quote.',1,true,false,'["Durable Metal Construction: Crafted from high-quality silver metal for a polished, upscale finish.", "Capless Swivel Design: Protects the USB connector without the need for a cap, offering convenience and durability.", "Rectangular Shape: Provides a modern and professional appearance that customers love.", "Perfect for Branding: Ideal for showcasing logos or designs, making it a standout promotional item.", "Compact and Portable: Lightweight and easy to carry, perfect for work, school, or travel."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "5.7cm W x 1.5cm H x 0.8cm L"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Silver", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/pat222/pat222-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,null,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/silver-metal-swivel-drive/');
