  ('IntexGlobal','PLAD01','Plastic Cups With Domed Cap Drink Bottle','plastic-cups-with-domed-cap-drink-bottle-plad01','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','The 470ml Plastic Cup with Domed Cap & Straw is a versatile and practical drinkware solution, ideal for smoothies, iced coffees, juices, and cold beverages. Designed for on-the-go convenience, this reusable cup is perfect for cafés, promotional events, and corporate giveaways.',250,true,false,'["470ml Capacity: Ideal for cold drinks, smoothies, and iced beverages.", "Durable Plastic Construction: Lightweight yet sturdy for everyday use.", "Domed Cap Design: Provides extra space for toppings like whipped cream.", "Reusable Straw Included: Ensures easy sipping and reduces waste.", "Perfect for Takeaway & Events: Great for cafés, juice bars, and branded promotions."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "10 (w) x 19 (h) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Custom", "hex": "", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,1.47,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/plastic-cups-with-domed-cap/');
