  ('IntexGlobal','PP731436','Milla Pouch Sunglasse','milla-pouch-sunglasse-pp731436','Outdoor & Lifestyle','Sunglasses','The Milla Pouch is the perfect blend of style and functionality, designed to keep your sunglasses safe and scratch-free. Lightweight and compact, it’s an ideal accessory for daily use or travel.',250,true,false,'["Soft and Durable Polyester Material: Provides a snug, scratch-resistant environment for your sunglasses.", "Lightweight and Compact: Effortlessly fits into your bag or pocket, offering convenient portability.", "Stylish Design: Combines practicality with a sleek look, suitable for any occasion.", "Versatile Use: Ideal for sunglasses, reading glasses, or small accessories."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "18 x 9 cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/pp731436/pp731436-black.webp"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/pp731436/pp731436-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/pp731436/pp731436-green.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/pp731436/pp731436-orange.webp"}, {"name": "Pink", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/pp731436/pp731436-pink.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/pp731436/pp731436-red.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/pp731436/pp731436-white.webp"}, {"name": "Yellow", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/s