  ('IntexGlobal','PS0088','Neoprene Sublimated Pencil Case','neoprene-sublimated-pencil-case-ps0088','Office & Desk','Pencil Cases','Introducing our Neoprene Sublimated Pencil Case, a versatile and durable solution for storing your stationery essentials. Designed with a sleek black zippered closure, this pencil case combines functionality with customizable style.',250,true,false,'["Premium Neoprene Material: Durable, lightweight, and resistant to wear, ensuring long-lasting use.", "Secure Zippered Closure: Features a sturdy black zipper to keep your items safely stored.", "Full-Color Sublimation: Customizable on both the front and back, offering vibrant and detailed branding or personal designs.", "Compact and Versatile: Perfect for storing pens, pencils, markers, and other small accessories for school, work, or travel."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "20cm L x 11.5cm W x 1cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps0088/ps0088-black.webp"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps0088/ps0088-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps0088/ps0088-green.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps0088/ps0088-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps0088/ps0088-orange.webp"}, {"name": "Purple", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps0088/ps0088-purple.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps0088/ps