  ('IntexGlobal','PS1005','Lazarus Plastic Pen','lazarus-plastic-pen-ps1005','Pens','Plastic Pens','Introducing the Lazarus Pen, a practical and stylish writing companion designed to leave a lasting impression. With its vibrant design and ergonomic features, this pen is the ideal promotional product for showcasing your brand.',100,true,false,'["Push/Click Action: Convenient and easy-to-use mechanism for smooth operation.", "Transparent Colored Barrel: Adds a modern and eye-catching look, perfect for promotional branding.", "Colored Rubber Grip: Ensures a comfortable writing experience, even during extended use.", "Shiny Silver Trim: Enhances the pen''s sleek and professional aesthetic.", "Compact Dimensions: Measuring 13.5cm x 1.5cm, it’s perfect for on-the-go use or desktop storage."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "13.5cm x 1.5cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1005/ps1005-black.webp"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1005/ps1005-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1005/ps1005-green.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1005/ps1005-orange.webp"}, {"name": "Purple", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1005/ps1005-purple.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1005/ps1005-red.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1005/ps1005-white.webp"}, {"name": "Yellow", "hex": "