  ('IntexGlobal','PS1101','Slimline Metal Pen','slimline-metal-pen-ps1101','Pens','Metal Pens','Introducing the Slimline Pen, a lightweight and ultra-slim writing companion designed for those who value convenience and style. Its sleek design makes it easy to attach to your clothing, ensuring it''s always within reach for instant note-taking.',100,true,false,'["Ultra-Slim Design: Lightweight and portable, perfect for clipping onto pockets or notebooks.", "Push/Click Action: Reliable mechanism for seamless writing on the go.", "Durable Aluminium Build: Ensures long-lasting performance with a premium matte finish.", "Elegant Silver Trimming: Adds a touch of sophistication to the modern design.", "Matte-Colored Barrel: Available in a variety of stylish colors to suit any preference or branding needs."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "14cm X 1cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1101/ps1101-black.webp"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1101/ps1101-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1101/ps1101-green.webp"}, {"name": "Pink", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1101/ps1101-pink.webp"}, {"name": "Purple", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1101/ps1101-purple.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1101/ps1101-red.webp"}, {"name": "Silver", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1101/ps1101-silver.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'suppli