  ('IntexGlobal','PS1115','Negan Metal Pen','negan-metal-pen-ps1115','Pens','Metal Pens','Introducing the Negan, a sophisticated and versatile writing tool designed for modern multitaskers. Crafted from durable metal with sleek black trim, this pen seamlessly transitions from traditional writing to digital device navigation.',100,true,false,'["Dual Purpose Design: Functions as a smooth-writing ballpen and a precise touch stylus for smartphones and tablets.", "Premium Metal Construction: Durable and stylish, offering a professional look and feel.", "Elegant Black Trim: Adds a touch of sophistication to the pen’s streamlined design.", "Black Ink: Equipped with high-quality black ink for everyday writing needs.", "Cross-Style Refillable: Reusable with Cross-style ink refills, making it an eco-friendly and long-lasting choice."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "14cm X 1.5cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Grey", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1115/ps1115-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/negan/');
