  ('IntexGlobal','PS1120','Extige Metal Pen','extige-metal-pen-ps1120','Pens','Metal Pens','Introducing the Extige Ballpen, a sophisticated writing instrument crafted exclusively for those who appreciate premium quality. Available only in black, this pen exudes elegance and professionalism, making it an exceptional promotional product for executive and high-end clientele.',100,true,false,'["Sleek Black Painted Barrel: Offers a refined and polished look, ideal for making a lasting impression.", "Premium Metal Construction: Durable and designed to withstand the demands of daily use while maintaining its luxurious appeal.", "Chrome Trim: Adds a striking contrast and a touch of sophistication to the pen’s design.", "Refillable Design: Compatible with Cross-style refills, ensuring long-lasting usability and eco-conscious practicality.", "Perfect for High-End Branding: An excellent choice for brands looking to cater to executives or upscale markets."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "14cm X 1.5cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1120/ps1120-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/extige/');
