  ('IntexGlobal','PS1208','Bamboo Grip Wheat Straw Pen','bamboo-grip-wheat-straw-pen-ps1208','Pens','Eco Pens','Introducing the Wheat Straw Pen with Bamboo Grip, a sustainable and functional writing tool designed for the modern professional. Its ultra-slim design makes it easy to carry and convenient for quick note-taking, while the bamboo grip provides a natural and comfortable feel.',100,true,true,'["Eco-Friendly Wheat Straw Barrel: Made from sustainable wheat straw, reducing environmental impact without sacrificing quality.", "Ultra-Slim Design: Lightweight and portable, ideal for clipping onto pockets or notebooks, ensuring convenience wherever you go.", "Push/Click Action: A reliable push mechanism that ensures smooth and seamless writing on the go.", "Natural Bamboo Grip: Adds a touch of nature to your writing experience while offering a comfortable and secure hold.", "Customizable: Ideal for branding, perfect as a promotional product to showcase your logo or message."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "1 x 13.7 cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1208/ps1208-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/bamboo-grip-wheat-straw-pen/');
