  ('IntexGlobal','PS1301','Mini Pencil Tube','mini-pencil-tube-ps1301','Pens','Pencils','Introducing the Mini Pencil Tube, a fun and practical promotional product perfect for schools, events, or as a branded giveaway. This compact tube contains a set of coloured pencils, offering a creative and portable solution for artists, kids, and anyone on the go. The tube can be easily customized with a sticker, making it an excellent promotional item for your brand.',100,true,false,'["Compact Tube: A small, portable container that’s easy to carry in bags or backpacks, perfect for travel or on-the-go creativity.", "Coloured Pencils: Comes with a set of vibrant, high-quality coloured pencils, great for sketching, drawing, or coloring activities.", "Sticker Application: Personalize the tube with your logo or design, making it an ideal promotional product for your brand.", "Fun and Functional: Perfect for schools, art projects, or as a giveaway at events, combining creativity with utility."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "3.5cm W x 10 cm H"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1301/ps1301-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1301/ps1301-green.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1301/ps1301-red.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1301/ps1301-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/mini-pencil-tube/');
