  ('IntexGlobal','PS1604','Aluminium Silver Pen Box Pen Presentation','aluminium-silver-pen-box-pen-presentation-ps1604','Pens','Pen Presentation','Introducing the Aluminium Silver Pen Box, a sophisticated and timeless packaging solution designed to elevate your promotional pens. With its sleek black exterior and elegant silver bezels, this box exudes luxury and professionalism, making it the perfect fit for high-end ballpoint pens.',100,true,false,'["Premium Design: The combination of a black exterior with silver bezels creates an elegant, upscale look that complements executive pens.", "Durable Aluminium Construction: Crafted from high-quality aluminium, ensuring both durability and a sleek, modern presentation.", "Perfect for Promotional Pens: Designed to fit a variety of executive-style pens, offering a sophisticated and secure way to present your promotional gifts.", "Ideal for Gifting: A classy and professional packaging choice that makes a lasting impression on clients, executives, or employees.", "Ballpen Sold Separately: The box is sold empty, allowing you to pair it with your chosen ballpoint pen for a fully personalized gift."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "16cm x 3cm x 2cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Silver", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1604/ps1604-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/aluminium-silver-pen-box/');
