  ('IntexGlobal','PS2002','Sunshine Coast Water Bottle - 750Ml','sunshine-coast-water-bottle-750ml-ps2002','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','Introducing the Sunshine Coast Water Bottle, a 750ml aluminium bottle designed for practicality and style. Featuring a screw top lid and a convenient carabiner, this BPA-free bottle is perfect for outdoor adventures, workouts, or everyday hydration.',50,true,false,'["750ml BPA-Free Aluminium Bottle: Lightweight and durable, perfect for keeping your drinks with you on the go.", "Screw Top Lid with Carabiner: Easy to carry and secure, ideal for attaching to bags or gear during activities.", "Available in 6 Colours: Choose from a variety of vibrant colours to suit your style or brand.", "Customizable: Perfect for rotary printing or laser engraving, making it a great promotional item or personalized gift.", "Not Suitable for Carbonated or Frozen Liquids: Best for still beverages.", "Not Recommended for Dishwasher Use: Hand wash to preserve the bottle’s appearance and functionality.", "Eco-Friendly Gift Box: Individually packed in a sustainable gift box, making it an excellent gift or branded product."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "7cm(dia) x 25cm(h)"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2002/ps2002-black.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2002/ps2002-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2002/ps2002-orange.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2002/ps2002-red.webp"}, {"name": "Silver", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2002/ps2002-silver.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2002/ps2002-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/sunshine-coast-water-bottle-750ml/');
