  ('IntexGlobal','PS2007','Bondi Vacuum Bottle - Steel Lid','bondi-vacuum-bottle-steel-lid-ps2007','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','Elevate your hydration game with the Bondi Vacuum Bottle, a perfect blend of durability, functionality, and sophistication. Featuring a sleek silver steel lid, this 500ml bottle is designed to keep your beverages at the ideal temperature while adding a touch of elegance to your daily routine.',50,true,false,'["500ml Double-Walled Stainless Steel Design: Ensures maximum insulation to keep drinks cold or hot for hours.", "Durable and BPA-Free: Safe for everyday use, with shatter and stain-resistant properties.", "Sleek Silver Lid: A stylish, secure lid that complements the bottle''s polished finish.", "Customizable for Branding: Ideal for rotary printing or laser engraving.", "Eco-Friendly Packaging: Individually packed in a sustainable gift box for a thoughtful presentation.", "Care Instructions: 1. Not suitable for dishwasher use. 2. Hand washing recommended to maintain quality and longevity."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "6.8cm(dia) x 25cm(h)"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2007/ps2007-black.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2007/ps2007-orange.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2007/ps2007-red.webp"}, {"name": "Royal", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2007/ps2007-royal.webp"}, {"name": "Silver", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2007/ps2007-silver.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/supplie