  ('IntexGlobal','PS2011','Bondi Wheat Straw Bottle','bondi-wheat-straw-bottle-ps2011','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','Make an eco-conscious choice with the Bondi Wheat Straw Bottle, crafted from natural wheat straw material. Perfect for everyday hydration, this 700ml bottle offers a durable and sustainable alternative to traditional plastic bottles.',50,true,false,'["Eco-Friendly Wheat Straw Material: Made from sustainable wheat straw, reducing plastic waste while offering a natural, earthy look.", "700ml Single-Walled Design: Lightweight and BPA-free, perfect for carrying your drinks on the go.", "Unique Finish: As each bottle is made from natural fibres, every bottle may have a slightly unique finish, adding to its charm.", "Shatter and Stain Resistant: Built to withstand everyday use and keep your bottle looking fresh.", "Not Suitable for Carbonated or Frozen Liquids: Best used with non-carbonated drinks.", "Not Recommended for Dishwasher Use: Hand wash to preserve the bottle’s longevity and quality.", "Eco-Friendly Gift Box: Individually packed in a sustainable gift box, making it perfect for gifting or promotional purposes."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "6.8cm Diameter x 25cm H"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2011/ps2011-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/bondi-wheat-straw-bottle/');
