  ('IntexGlobal','PS2012','Brit Bottle - 500ML Double Wall','brit-bottle-500ml-double-wall-ps2012','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','Make your brand stand out with the Brit Vacuum Bottle 500ml, a premium promotional product that combines elegance, functionality, and sustainability. Perfect for corporate gifts, events, or giveaways, this bottle is designed to impress.',50,true,false,'["Sophisticated Design: Featuring a premium soft-feel rubber finish and available in a variety of stylish colours.", "Durable & BPA-Free: Made from double-walled stainless steel, ensuring long-lasting use and safety.", "Superior Insulation: Keeps drinks cold for up to 24 hours or hot for up to 12 hours, making it ideal for every season.", "Shatter & Stain Resistant: Built to handle daily use while maintaining a clean and polished appearance.", "Perfect for Branding: Customizable with rotary printing or engraving, including a stunning shiny gloss finish to showcase your logo or message.", "Eco-Friendly Packaging: Each bottle is individually packed in a sustainable gift box.", "Care Instructions: Not suitable for carbonated or frozen liquids. Hand washing recommended to preserve the premium finish."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "7.3cm Diameter x 22.5cm H"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Baby Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2012/ps2012-baby-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Baby Pink", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2012/ps2012-baby-pink.webp"}, {"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2012/ps2012-black.webp"}, {"name": "Bottle Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2012/ps2012-bottle-green.webp"}, {"name": "Charcoal", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04