  ('IntexGlobal','PS2022','Banks Tumbler 300ml Coffee Cup','banks-tumbler-300ml-coffee-cup-ps2022','Drinkware','Coffee Cups','Introducing 300ml Banks Stainless Steel Tumbler, designed for style and functionality. With its matte powder-coated finish and brushed stainless steel bottom, it’s the perfect blend of durability and sophistication.',50,true,false,'["300ml Capacity: Ideal for a generous serving of coffee, tea, or any preferred beverage.", "Matte Powder-Coated Finish: The matte black coating not only provides a sleek, modern look but also ensures a comfortable grip.", "Brushed Stainless Steel Bottom: Offers a striking contrast and added durability.", "Tapered Design: The wider top and narrower bottom create an elegant profile while maintaining stability.", "Stainless Steel Construction: Built to last and offers excellent thermal retention to keep your drinks at the perfect temperature for longer.", "Compact Size: Height: 11.5cm, Top Diameter: 8.6cm, Bottom Diameter: 7.3cm.", "Eco-Friendly Packaging: Each tumbler comes individually packed in a kraft paper box, making it an eco-conscious choice."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "11.5(h) cm x 8.6(d) cm - 7.3(d) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2022/ps2022-black.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2022/ps2022-navy.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2022/ps2022-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/banks-tumbler-300ml/');
