  ('IntexGlobal','PS2031','Vacuum Cup','vacuum-cup-ps2031','Drinkware','Coffee Cups','Introducing the 350ml Vacuum Cup, a premium solution for keeping your beverages hot and fresh. Combining double-wall, vacuum-insulated stainless steel with thoughtful design, this cup is as functional as it is stylish.',50,true,false,'["350ml Capacity: Perfectly sized for a satisfying serving of coffee, tea, or any hot beverage.", "Double-Wall Vacuum Insulation: Ensures drinks stay hot for extended periods, making it ideal for busy days or commutes.", "Sleek Finish: Features a flat-painted exterior for a modern aesthetic and a comfortable, slip-resistant grip.", "Two Lid Options:  - Secure Screw-On Flat Lid: Leakproof and travel-friendly.  - Wide Top Opening: For convenient sipping and easy access.", "Eco-Friendly Packaging: Presented in an individual natural box, making it an excellent gift option.", "Care Instructions: Hand washing is recommended to maintain the cup’s durability and finish; not dishwasher safe."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "Dia 6.7 cm x 17 H cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2031/ps2031-black.webp"}, {"name": "Cream", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2031/ps2031-cream.webp"}, {"name": "Teal", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2031/ps2031-teal.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/vacuum-cup/');
